import React from "react";
import { Container, Grid, Card, CardContent, Typography, Button, LinearProgress, Box, Avatar } from "@mui/material";
import { Star, EmojiEvents, TrendingUp } from "@mui/icons-material";

const Dashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" style={{ marginTop: "20px" }}>
      {/* Header Dashboard */}
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>Selamat Datang di Dashboard BioFun!</Typography>
      <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="textSecondary">Halo, Pengguna! Siap untuk petualangan biologi hari ini?</Typography>

      {/* Progress Overview */}
      <Grid container spacing={3} style={{ marginTop: "20px" }}>
        {/* Learning Path */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Jalur Pembelajaran</Typography>
              <LinearProgress variant="determinate" value={25} style={{ marginTop: "10px", height: "10px" }} />
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" style={{ marginTop: "5px" }}>25% selesai pada Sistem Pencernaan</Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Achievements */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Pencapaian & Lencana</Typography>
              <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" marginTop="10px">
                <Avatar style={{ backgroundColor: "#FFD700", marginRight: "10px" }}><EmojiEvents /></Avatar>
                <Typography variant="body2">Master Fotosintesis</Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" marginTop="10px">
                <Avatar style={{ backgroundColor: "#90CAF9", marginRight: "10px" }}><Star /></Avatar>
                <Typography variant="body2">Penjelajah Biologi</Typography>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Interactive Cards */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Hewan</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">Jelajahi dunia hewan yang penuh dengan keajaiban!</Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="primary" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>Mulai</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Tumbuhan</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">Pelajari lebih dalam tentang tumbuhan dan fotosintesis!</Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="primary" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>Mulai</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Tubuh Manusia</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">Eksplorasi bagaimana tubuh manusia bekerja!</Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="primary" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>Mulai</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Daily Biology Fact and Challenge */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Fakta Harian Menarik</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>
                Tahukah kamu? Tubuh manusia memiliki lebih dari 37 triliun sel!
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Tantangan Harian</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>
                Jawab tantangan harian ini dan dapatkan poin tambahan!
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>Ikuti Tantangan</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Leaderboard */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Papan Peringkat</Typography>
              <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" marginTop="10px">
                <TrendingUp color="primary" />
                <Typography variant="body2" style={{ marginLeft: "10px" }}>Top 10% Penjelajah BioFun</Typography>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Personalized Recommendations */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Modul yang Disarankan</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>
                Berdasarkan riwayat belajar, kami merekomendasikan "Eksperimen Pertumbuhan Tumbuhan".
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="primary" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>Mulai Belajar</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Target Mingguan</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>
                Selesaikan 3 permainan tentang Kerajaan Hewan minggu ini!
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="primary" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: "10px" }}>Mulai</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
